I cannot think of remarriage: Hrithik Roshan.
Hrithik Roshan and Sussanne Khan's romance was the stuff of legend. The childhood sweethearts' marriage gave us goals for over thirteen years, and their separation was a major jolt. But it has been a while since their divorce, and fans are keen to see their favourite superhero tie the knot again.PHOTOS: Ex-wife Sussanne Khan joins Hrithik Roshan for his birthday bash